titleInfo.title: USA v. Hernandez-Acosta
titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT as to Abel Hernandez-Acosta. The defendant plead guilty to Count I of the Indictment and is sentenced to the custody of the Bureau of Prisons for 8 months; The defendant shall be given credit for time served from 10/8/06; 3 years Supervised Release with special conditions; $100.00 Special Assessment (remitted on the motion of the government). Criminal Case Terminated as to defendant Abel Hernandez-Acosta. Ordered by Judge Joseph F. Bataillon. - (4 cc to USM) (KBJ)
